(Computer Running Slow) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Keywords: computer slow laptop slow system slow performance lag freezing) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Steps to fix a slow computer:) Tj T*
(1. Restart your computer to clear memory and temp files.) Tj T*
(2. Close unused programs and browser tabs.) Tj T*
(3. Check Task Manager \(Ctrl+Shift+Esc\) for high CPU or memory usage.) Tj T*
(4. Run Disk Cleanup: search Disk Cleanup in Start menu.) Tj T*
(5. Disable startup programs: Task Manager > Startup tab.) Tj T*
(6. Check for Windows updates and install pending ones.) Tj T*
(7. Run a full antivirus scan to check for malware.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(If still slow:) Tj T*
(- Check if hard disk is nearly full \(keep 15% free space\).) Tj T*
(- Consider upgrading RAM if consistently above 90% usage.) Tj T*
(- Contact IT for hardware assessment.) Tj T*
